content: असिक्नी [सिता केशादौ शुभ्रा जरती, तद्भिन्ना अवृद्धा, सित-क्नादेशः ङीप् च <ls>P. IV. 1. 39</ls> <ab>Vārt.</ab>] {@--1@} A young maid-servant of the harem. {@--2@} Night (<ls>Nir.</ls>). {@--3@} <ab>N.</ab> of a river in the Punjaub, mentioned along with others in the line इमं मे गंगे यमुने &c.
